    "note": "Design-first artifact only \u2014 describes the MCP tool surface, not a running server. Tool input/output schemas $ref the same object schemas as the OpenAPI; each tool maps to an OpenAPI operationId. Surfaces the Queens Borough President functions (community boards and appointments, land-use/ULURP recommendations, discretionary funding, events, press releases) and adds apply_to_community_board \u2014 the net-new write workflow that today lives only as an HTML/PDF form.",
